{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2156830/extras/WoY-MasterVillainDuel-616x346.png?t=1735897565\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Discover the meaning of the <strong>Word of Yendor</strong> in these procedurally generated adventures, set in a steamgoth world of magic and steam contraptions. If you dare, also explore the secrets of the <i>White Steam</i> or the <i>Black Smoke</i> perspectives.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore settlements, solve word puzzles, and find your way to the local Master Villains usurping crucial elements of the mystery. Use your word-solving skills to navigate dangerous obstacles and gather resources. Engage in turn-based word duels against opponents with a unique tactical combat system.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Each story ending is tailor-made, offering a personalized experience. How is this possible? By leveraging the world's most powerful content creation system! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2156830/extras/WoY-Scout-616x346.png?t=1735897565\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2156830/extras/header-features.png?t=1735897565\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Turn-based, procedurally generated adventures</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Detailed, highly configurable hero/heroine portraits</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Multiple types of word puzzles and word duels, forged into a coherent game system</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Duel opponents that also compose words from the same pool of letters as you</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Words that can literally hurt or mend</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Mini-adventures in space-time and in the afterworld</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Collection and crafting of items and upgrades, as well as optional theft and trade of poignant curios</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Dynamic, often dramatic or humorous story, yet it\u2019s always meaningful and personal</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2156830/extras/WoY-SuspiciousAccident-616x346.png?t=1735897565\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2156830/extras/header-technical-facts.png?t=1735897565\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> A typical adventure can be completed in 30\u201390 minutes, depending on the complexity level of your choice. Just like a game of chess, Words of Yendor offers endless replayability, providing unique and thrilling adventures each time you play.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Your progress is automatically saved, allowing you to contemplate the challenges for as long as you like. The game remains unaffected by the passage of real time.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Note that embracing the spirit of roguelikes, this is also a \u201cpermadeath\u201d game, so if your hero falls, the game is over. However, if you enter the same <i>adventure seed</i> number, you can replay any adventure as many times as you want.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> It's never just one of the \u201cred, green, blue\u201d endings. Each one is personal and unique!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2156830/extras/WoY-Showdown-616x346.png?t=1735897565\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_as